    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hey @chrissshh,\r\n\r\nThis is because the custom router was made for the `pages` directory router.\r\n\r\nFrom my experience when doing CSR with the `app` dir, simply having `<InstantSearch routing={true}>` works out of the box as Next.js no longer relies on having a specific key in history to know whether it should rerender when back/forward browser button has been pressed.\r\n\r\nCan you please tell me what's not working with `routing={true}` ?\r\n\r\nThe reason we don't document it is that we still don't support SSR with the `app` dir, but maybe it's worth documenting that for CSR.",
