    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hey @ddaoxuan and @chrissshh !\r\n\r\nWe released an experimental package for App Router support, and it supports routing already : https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/going-further/server-side-rendering/react/#app-router-experimental\r\nYou can activate routing simply by adding a `routing` boolean prop to `InstantSearchNext`.\r\n\r\nI'll close this as it's now solved !",
